To place a marker in [[Digital Performer]] move the song position pointer where you would like the marker to be placed, then use the key command '''Control-M'''.

You can access the Markers window by going to '''Project/Markers''' or using the key command '''Shift K'''.


[[File:Digital Performer marker display.png]]



